Tavatron:

Tavatron placed a gentle hand against Dinobot's arm, concern and worry 
etched on her face. Suddenly a dull pain began to radiate through her 
stomach. It was barely noticable, but still, it shouldn't be there. Dinobot 
had made sure of that. No matter, she would worry about it later:

"Dinobot, are you alright?" Tavatron placed her other hand against Dinobot's 
clenched fist. The pain in her stomach had intensified, but it was not of 
any importance. She would survive. Tavatron heard Iron over her com:

"C'mon, let's get back to the ark." Tavatron shouldered her staff, all the 
while keeping a concerned hand on Dinobot's shoulder. It was obvious he was 
in pain, but why didn't he say something?

Tavatron placed her other hand on her stomach. What was wrong with it? It 
shouldn't hurt. Her internal comp said that her systems were at full power, 
so why did it hurt? No matter, it was only a dull pain, nothing important.

(OOC: Sorry if I missed any important posts or anything, I'm really tired 
and kinda out of it. If there's anything that concerns Tav that I failed to 
reply to please let me know. Thanx!)
